Konidela Ram Charan Teja is an Indian actor, producer, and entrepreneur who works predominantly in Telugu cinema. One of the highest-paid actors in India, he is the recipient of several awards, including three Filmfare Awards and two Nandi Awards. Since 2013, he has featured in Forbes India's Celebrity 100 list. Wikipedia
Born: 27 March 1985 (age 37 years), Chennai
Height: 1.74 m
Spouse: Upasana Kamineni (m. 2012)
Parents: Chiranjeevi, Surekha Konidala
Siblings: Sreeja Kalyan, Sushmitha
